Class CustomerWebService

  • java.lang.Object
    • webServices.CustomerWebService

  • @RestController
public class CustomerWebService
extends java.lang.Object
    In this class there is all the Methods ("CRUD" operations) that a customer account can get access to by request over http protocol from the cleintSide. this class making use by "Http servlet request"
